{"title":"Wild-looking Ryuger Eidolon Covid eBike is a full suspension carbon… commuter?","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/25/wild-looking-ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-is-a-full-suspension-carbon-commuter/","date":1616693498000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Dear me, there’s a lot to unpack here. Australian brand Ryuger have announced that their latest wild-looking creation is about to go into production. Meet the Ryuger Eidolon BR-RTS, a full carbon, full suspension, aero commuter ebike. We’ve never seen anything quite like it…</p><p>Why do they call it their Covid eBike? Simply because they developed it over the lockdown period, during the Covid pandemic.</p><h2>Ryuger Eidolon BR-RTS</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x334/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"ryuger eidolon carbon aero ebike full suspension carbon frame\" width=\"1200\" height=\"829\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x334/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-297x205.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/upl