021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-800x553.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-120x83.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-768x531.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-218x150.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 218w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-696x481.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-1068x738.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-608x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 608w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25122235/ryuger-eidolon-ebike-full-suspension-carbon-commuter-100x70.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 100w\"></a></p><p>I feel the Ryuger Eidolon ebike bears some resemblance to a full suspension mountain bike, aero time trial bike, and a MotoGP bike, all at the same time. On paper, it is in fact a commuter ebike, but that classification does this creation something of a disservice.</p><p>For starters, it fails to consider the carbon frame and fork with aero shaped tubes and blades, and the Cane Creek coil shock-damped front and rear suspension. We don’t yet know how much front and rear wheel travel this thing has, but we’ll update you as soon as we’ve heard back from Ryuger.</p><figure id=\"attachment_253632\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-253632\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike.jpg\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng%3Awebp%2Fngcb8%2Frs%3Adevice%2Frscb8-1\" alt=\"ryuger eidolon covid ebike road aero mtb rear shock\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-696x464.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/25110903/ryuger-eidolon-covid-ebike-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-253632\">The complete bike weighs a claimed 19kg</figcaption></figure><p>The few pictures shared with us show very little of the finer detail. We don’t have many angles on this thing so much of this will be speculation.</p><figure id=\"attachment_253645\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-253645\"><a hr